{"type": "article", "id": 25764, "title": "他设计这么多房子，共同点是爱用竹子做成一棵树的样子", "description": "这次的柱子较之前的柱子更加方正和粗旷，富有野趣。", "date": "2016-04-21T07:37:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3967, "name": "餐厅"}, {"id": 26510, "name": "武重义建筑事务所"}, {"id": 26511, "name": "武重义"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 171, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702142228fIRLzt8G2mxH1Ppg.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>武重义（vo trong nghia）是目前越南最受瞩目的设计师之一，他利用竹材料设计建筑获得了包括<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/1305.html\">“亚洲建筑师协会 2014 年建筑奖”</a>等多个奖项。因为早年求学于日本，回到越南后所设计的建筑多和这种产于亚洲的材料有关，渐渐也形成了自己的个人风格。</p>\n<p>“竹子就是二十一世纪的钢铁，我的初衷是，竹子又便宜又好看，很耐用，非常环保。”</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142212H4vaZfqrJpKzX6m3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Eco-resort，河内</div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021422125FXYxvyHI73ULGfA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">墨西哥 Jardines de 餐厅</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142213BE5dOU74jmtTPcwb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">米兰世博会越南馆</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021422149Gqt7iyrg56xCKXs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">胡志明市 Naman 度假村</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>这所竹餐厅<a href=\"http://votrongnghia.com/projects/roc-von-restaurant/\"> roc von restaurant </a>是武重义的新作，它位于首都河内通向和平市（hoa binh）的路上，距河内有 30 公里，是汽车和游客停留的中转站以及河内人周末一日游的地方。</p>\n<p>餐厅沿着环形的湖泊边缘而建，呈现月牙形，左右对称。中间延伸了一个圆形的观景台，是悬在湖面上的。实际上，这个餐厅更像是一条走廊或者茶园。12 个用竹子搭建的方型的柱子在上方散开成屋顶，呈现出参天大树的感觉。桌椅就围绕着柱子排布着，竹子做的灯从柱子上垂下来，绿色植物点缀其中，是一个四面通透又可以乘凉的好地方。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142214FoBizJIOE6Cwpqey.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142215rsIwEz476daQbCSv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021422154tAM3HieydxTZqCg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070214221651HmgVa7lxWqjheo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53789731\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142216BPWYXOf7oCQ2ERNK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142217h75HUm3QF2G06xcS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142217y0VoZtlBOKI9MS7D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>与之前的建筑一样，搭建这些柱子要使用两种材料，一种称为 Luong ，更加强壮而耐用，作为柱子。另一种称为 Tam Vong，更具柔韧性，用作上方的屋顶。他们还使用传统的编织和保护方法，确保能长期使用。而这次的柱子较之前的柱子更加方正和粗犷，富有野趣。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142218bRvytYVm4pJqrxDd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61369193\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142218pTCec18bolAuwnPr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142219FdAM6WS5kpNDgBsV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4596577\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">到了晚上，黄色的灯光顺着一排竹制的柱子将倒影投射在湖面上，给人格外的宁静自然。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142220qrJVfQoemOzpgTdl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142221kPvWCmyL2d0DRNlq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021422257sbCpPKoYdOe3vmI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.29722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142225moDwt0jaWYJ25UzX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.26296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142226FIGqTLXPSv80lRJQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.18703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/vo-trong-nghia-architects-roc-von-restaurant-bamboo-hanoi-vietnam-04-19-2016/\"> designboom</a></p>\n\n"}